1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,680
Njagala okukulaga engeri gy'oyinza okunoonyereza ku kintu kyonna kubanga okunoonyereza buyinza.

2
00:00:05,680 --> 00:00:10,000
Ate era, bw'oyiga okukikola, osobola okweyigiriza.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:11,000
kyonna ky'oyagala.

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:14,760
Era singa tukizuula nti abantu abasinga obungi tebamanyi ngeri y'okunoonyerezaamu, bamanyi engeri

5
00:00:14,760 --> 00:00:15,760
okunoonya.

6
00:00:15,760 --> 00:00:19,880
Era waliwo enjawulo ey'amaanyi kubanga bw'onookunoonya, ojja kwesigama ku balala

7
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:22,440
abantu okukulowoozaako era ekyo tetukyagala.

8
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:23,840
Twetaaga okukola obulungi.

9
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:26,080
N'olwekyo, okunoonyereza kulimu ebitundu bingi.

10
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:29,560
Enkola gye nkozesa erimu nnya, era nja kukutegeeza.

11
00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:31,680
Ekimu ku byo kwe kunoonya ebweru.

12
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:35,600
Wano we we weetaaga okutandikira, naye era w'olekera abantu abasinga obungi.

13
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:41,760
Eno y'okunoonyereza kwo mu Google, vidiyo za TikTok, okunnyonnyola kwa YouTube, eby'okuddamu bya AI.

14
00:00:41,760 --> 00:00:46,519
Era ekizibu eky'okuyimirira wano kiri nti ofuna enkomerero ez'amaanyi era oli

15
00:00:46,519 --> 00:00:48,640
nga tebamanyi ngeri gye zaazimbibwamu.

16
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:49,640
Ka tukole ekyokulabirako.

17
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:55,000
Ka tugambe nti okunoonyereza ku bintu eby'ekizikiza n'ofuna ebivaamu nga,

18
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:57,600
ekikola ku bitundu 85 ku buli kikumi eky'obwengula.

19
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,760
Tetukiraba.

20
00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:00,520
Kino kikwata ku bukulu bw'ebintu.

21
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:05,120
Otegeera ebintu ebyo byonna, naye tosobola kutegeera bintu ng'ebyo.

22
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:11,440
ekyaliwo oba obujulizi bwa ngeri ki obwesigamiziddwa ku ekyo oba n'endowooza za ngeri ki eziri mu mpaka?

23
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:13,480
Kati olwo oyinza otya okukyusa omuwendo 1 mu ngeri entuufu?

24
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:17,400
Okikozesa ng'obulagirizi bwo so si ng'obuyigirize.

25
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:23,560
N'olwekyo, ekiruubirirwa kyo ku kigero kino kirina okuba eky'okuyiga ebigambo, n'okumanya ebigambo ebikulu.

26
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:27,760
n'okwongera okwebuuza ebibuuzo, n'okutegeera by'otomanyi.

27
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,920
ky'okyalina okwegomba okumanya.

28
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:34,800
Oyinza okumala eddakiika 10 oba 15 ng'onoonyereza ku kifo ekisooka.

29
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:39,000
Era n'olekera awo okwebuuza, kiki kye nkyalemererwa okutegeera?

30
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:42,160
Era ekibuuzo ekyo kye mulyango gwo oguyingira mu kifo eky'okubiri.

31
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:44,760
Ekitundu eky'okubiri kwe kweyongerayongera ku nsibuko.

32
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:47,160
Wano we watandikira okunoonyereza.

33
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,760
Kati olwo kino kirabika kitya?

34
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:51,880
Kino kivvuunula ensibuko n'ebitundu.

35
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:55,520
Asoma ebitundu byonna mu kifo ky'okuwandiika ebyawandiikibwa.

36
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:59,120
Ekimu ku byo kwe kugoberera ennyiriri n'ebiwandiiko.

37
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,520
Guno gwe lugenda okuva.

38
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,520
Kino kye ki?

39
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:03,520
Kino kyava wa?

40
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:05,680
Ka tuddemu ku kyokulabirako ky'ebintu eby'ekizikiza.

41
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:08,640
Kati tokyabeera ku Google oba ku TikTok.

42
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:10,759
Oteekawo olupapula lwa NASA.

43
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,640
Okyuka ku kunoonyereza okukoleddwa.

44
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:18,520
Oteekawo okunoonyereza kw'ekizikiza kya Galaxy Rotation Curve era olabye okuzuula kwa

45
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,520
bannasayansi.

46
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:24,400
N'olwekyo, kino kikulu nnyo kubanga kati olaba obujulizi so si ndowooza yokka.

47
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:28,080
Kati olwo oyinza otya okuggula ebintu byonna mu ngeri entuufu?

48
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,640
Tokoma ku kusoma olupapula olwo ne luggwaawo.

49
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:33,600
Osaanidde okuba n'ebitabo ebisooka okuva ku bitaano okutuuka ku kkumi ebya buli kimu ky'otunuulira.

50
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:36,400
Mu kiseera kino olina okugoberera ebiwandiiko.

51
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:41,760
N'olwekyo, okuva mu kitundu kino okutuuka ku kunoonyereza okutuuka ku byawandiikibwa ebisooka, buli kimu kiba kirungi nnyo.

52
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,760
Waliwo akakwate konna.

53
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:49,760
Osaanidde okukulembeza ebiwandiiko bya.edu's.gov, ebifulumizibwa, ekintu kyonna ekiva eri omukugu mu by'obufuzi.

54
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,760
ennimiro.

55
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:56,000
Era wandyebuuzizza nti, kigambo ki kino kye nsinziira okunoonyerezaako?

56
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:59,799
Kubanga bw'oba tosobola kuddamu ekyo, oyinza okuba ng'okyali ku ddaala erisooka.

57
00:02:59,799 --> 00:03:02,959
Nnyingira mu kifo eky'okusatu, ekitegeeza okumanya engeri z'ebintu.

58
00:03:02,959 --> 00:03:07,519
Era ndowooza nti kino kye kigero amazima mwe gatandika okulabika kubanga

59
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:13,040
Ku ntikko eno, essira lyo erisinga okuligeraageranya ku nsibuko ezitali zimu era oli mwetoowaze.

60
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:16,000
okutegana n'obutategeeragana wakati waabwe.

61
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:19,880
Otegeera ebintu by'olaba nga bikyuse.

62
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:25,200
Ounoonya ebintu ebilabika enfunda n'enfunda mu nsi ezo, oba

63
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:31,480
bye bimu ku bibala, ebibuuzo, n'endowooza oba ensonga kubanga biraga nti bya mugaso.

64
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:35,160
Ka tugambe nti wasoma ebitabo mukaaga ebyogera ku bintu eby'ekizikiza.

65
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:39,359
Era mukaaga ku bo baagamba nti enjuyi y'eggye lya Galaxy terikwatagana n'obunene obulabika era omu ku bo

66
00:03:39,359 --> 00:03:41,800
Yagamba nti oboolyawo amateeka ga gravity galemereddwa.

67
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:46,280
N'olwekyo, kati olaba obumu obukolebwa mu nsonga eyo.

68
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:51,240
Bw'olaba ebisaanyizo n'obukakafu obuliwo, otandika okufuna endowooza ennuŋŋamu.

69
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:53,280
n'okutegeera by'oyiga.

70
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:56,720
Ku kigero kyonna, esatu mu ngeri entuufu, okunoonya okukwatagana.

71
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:59,000
Kati olwo abantu abasinga obungi bakkiriziganya ku ki?

72
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,640
Ate era olina okukiraba nti waliwo obutategeeragana.

73
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:05,720
N'olwekyo, lowooza ku ngeri bannassaayansi gye baawukanamu ku nsonga eyo.

74
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,920
Osaanidde okukakasa obujulizi bw'ofuna.

75
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:11,880
Osobola okugiggyamu obujulizi obw'amaanyi n'obw'okulowooza.

76
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:17,039
Osobola n'okuteekawo ebikonde bisatu eby'ebirowoozo oba okubiwandiika bw'oba oyagala.

77
00:04:17,039 --> 00:04:22,039
Naye ekimu ku byo kwe kumanya kw'ofuna okukwatagana n'ebyawandiikibwa byonna.

78
00:04:22,039 --> 00:04:27,680
Ekirala ku bikwata ku bubaka obwesigamiziddwa ku nsonga era ekirala ku bikwata ku bubaka obwesigamiziddwa ku nsonga ezitali zimu.

79
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:32,020
Bw'okola bw'otyo, osobola okweyigiriza n'okuzimba endowooza yo.

80
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:33,720
okusalawo ku nsonga eyo.

81
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:38,960
Omutindo gw'obunnya n'omutindo gw'ekitebe kubanga wano we weelekera awo okuyiga obubaka

82
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:41,800
n'otandika okulowooza mu nkola.

83
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,520
Obuuza ebibuuzo ebirungi.

84
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:48,400
Ozimba ebyokulabirako eby'ebirowoozo by'omutwe gw'ofuba okunoonyerezaako era otandika

85
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:52,800
Okugatta ebirowoozo ku bifo eby'enjawulo eby'okunoonyereza.

86
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:58,000
N'olwekyo, olina okunoonya enkola ekwata ku nsonga yonna gy'ofuba okunoonyerezaamu.

87
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:02,680
Mu kifo ky'okubuuza eky'ekizikiza kye ki, tubuuza ebibuuzo eby'omunda.

88
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:08,000
Tubuuza ebintu gamba nga lwaki gravity etera okweyisa bw'etyo oba ndowooza ki ezikoleddwa

89
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:13,480
mu nteekateeka yaffe eyaliwo ey'ekizikiza eky'ekizikiza oba ekyandibadde kituufu olw'ebyo byonna

90
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,480
Okuba nti oli mu nsobi.

91
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:20,360
Ofuba okwetendeka okulowooza ennyo n'okubuuza ebibuuzo ebisingako obulungi.

92
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:22,360
kikulu nnyo mu kunoonyereza.

93
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:27,880
Mu kifo ky'okubuuza ebibuuzo eby'omutendera ogw'okubiri, tetubuuza kiki kyokka, naye lwaki era lwaki.

94
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:31,160
Watya singa tuzimba ku byokulabirako byaffe eby'ebirowoozo?

95
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:34,120
N'olwekyo, fuba okutwala ekipande ky'olupapula n'okukiwandiika mu maaso go, si bwe kiri?

96
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:37,120
Ebintu eby'ekizikiza, kye kifo eky'okufiirwa by'ebisaanyizo.

97
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,000
Kiggibwa mu bikolwa eby'obuyigirize.

98
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:41,200
Tekitegerekeka butereevu.

99
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:44,920
Ggyayo waggulu olabe mmapa n'otandika okugigatta.

100
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,080
Ebintu eby'ekizikiza bya sayansi.

101
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,240
Kikulu nnyo mu by'obwengula.

102
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,280
Kye bufirosoofo bw'enzikiriza.

103
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:54,960
Osobola okutwala obubaka bw'olina n'obutwala mu bujulizi, obutategeerekeka,

104
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:58,559
Ekikwata ku nsonga eno kwe kuba nti tetumanyi bya maanyi nnyo.

105
00:05:58,559 --> 00:06:02,599
Bw'otandika okugitegeka mu maaso go era n'otandika okugitegeka

106
00:06:02,599 --> 00:06:06,320
buli kintu kyonna ekikwatagana n'otandika okulaba obutaliimu.

107
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:10,159
N'ekyewuunyisa kiri nti ekyo kikuyamba okukitegeera obulungi.

108
00:06:10,159 --> 00:06:13,599
Okunoonyereza kulaga nti tekuli mu ntegeka y'obutonde, wabula kuli mu ntegeka.

109
00:06:13,599 --> 00:06:17,719
N'olwekyo, okunoonyereza, n'okwongera, n'okugeraageranya, n'okuzimba endowooza ezo.

110
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,720
abazannyi.

111
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:21,240
Era okuva ku byokulabirako ebyo eby'ebirowoozo ojja kufuna ebibuuzo ebirungi.

112
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:25,640
Era n'okiddamu nate n'ebibuuzo ebisingako obulungi by'onoonya era n'okwongera

113
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:28,680
era n'ogeraageranya era n'ozimba emizingo emirala.

114
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:31,720
Era bw'otyo bw'oyiga okulowooza wekka.

115
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:34,680
Bw'otyo bw'otandika okutegeera ekintu.

116
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:39,000
Bw'otyo bw'otandika okukwatagana n'okwegomba kwo.

